  "game": {
    "title": "POOL ROOM BILLIARD",
    "description": "Using two Joy-Con™ 2 controllers delivers the authentic feel of striking a cue ball in real billiards!\n\nEnjoy authentic 8-ball and 9-ball games in a stylish pool bar atmosphere.\n\nPlay online matches against players worldwide!\nQuick Match lets you play instantly, while Room Match lets you create rooms by choosing game, rules, and opponents, or join existing rooms for easy online play anytime, with anyone!\nPlus, you can play mini-games against the CPU during matchmaking wait times—a nice touch for comfortable online play.\n\nSolo players get the robust “VSCOM Mode” and “Tournament Mode.” In “VS 2P Mode,” use one Joy-Con™ 2 controller each for quick 1P vs. 2P matches!\n\nExperience authentic 3D online billiards, uniquely optimized for Nintendo Switch™ 2! Enjoy stylish, rich visuals, dynamic replay effects, C-button chat during matches, and intuitive mouse-like controls.",
